            "content": "<p>Our unique design features interlocking rings so you have a piece of eachother wherever you go.</p><p>These rings represent being together no matter what, even when you're far apart. They're perfect for couples who are far away and want to feel close, or for those ready to show their commitment. Anyone can wear them to show how much they care about each other. With our special rings, you can say \"I promise\" and celebrate your love together.</p>",
